cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with computer vision tasks related to video analysis, specifically human action recognition. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a new operation for capturing temporal-spatial information, which involves deep learning models, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper deals with video-related tasks, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). The proposed method involves attention models, which could also fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
